snippet.title: Emergency - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Emergency is a free-to-play multiplayer strategy game where players embody an incident coordinator developed by Sixteen Tons Entertainment. Players are tasked with coordinating with other players to deal with fires, make arrests against criminals, and rescue those who are in need. Emergency is launching in summer 2023 for PC.
